  <walkingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Lugano is the perfect place for a leisurely stroll along the lakeside, or amidst the cobbled streets of the old town. A favourite is the weekly ‘Parks and Gardens’ guided walking tour around the town. More energetic walkers can take one of the several funiculars up into the hills to follow the challenging walking trails through the colourful landscape. The Monte Bré, accessible by funicular offers a variety of well-marked trails from gentle walks to more difficult trails up to the peaks. A free guided weekly walk at the summit usually takes place on Fridays.</p>]]></walkingDescription>
